arm_group.description:
(IV dose at 0.3 mg/kg, 1.0 mg/kg, 2.5 mg/kg, or 5.0 mg/kg and subcutaneous dose at 150 mg)
Participants will receive GS-5745 as follows:
SAD cohort - single IV dose;
MAD cohort - multiple (three) IV doses every two weeks;
Adaptive MAD cohort - a single subcutaneous dose for 5 consecutive weeks

Participants will receive placebo to match GS-5745 as follows:
SAD cohort - single IV dose;
MAD cohort - multiple (three) IV doses every two weeks;
Participants will receive GS-5745 150 mg as follows:
Adaptive MAD cohort - a single subcutaneous dose for 5 consecutive weeks
